      "updated": 1775707748533,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. System initializes with users, songs, artists, albums, playlists\n2. User signs up / logs in\n3. User searches for song/artist/album\n4. System returns matching results\n5. User selects a song\n6. System validates:\n   - Song exists\n   - User access (free/premium)\n7. Song is added to user's play queue\n8. Music player starts playing the song\n9. While playing:\n   - User can pause/resume/skip\n10. If song ends:\n    - Next song from queue is played\n11. User can like the song\n12. User can add song to a playlist\n13. Playlist gets updated\n14. System stores play history\n15. Recommendations get updated based on history\n16. If queue becomes empty:\n    - Autoplay suggested songs OR stop\n17. Repeat until user session ends",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. System initializes with users, songs, artists, albums, playlists\n2. User signs up / logs in\n3. User searches for song/artist/album\n4. System returns matching results\n5. User selects a song\n6. System validates:\n   - Song exists\n   - User access (free/premium)\n7. Song is added to user's play queue\n8. Music player starts playing the song\n9. While playing:\n   - User can pause/resume/skip\n10. If song ends:\n    - Next song from queue is played\n11. User can like the song\n12. User can add song to a playlist\n13. Playlist gets updated\n14. System stores play history\n15. Recommendations get updated based on history\n16. If queue becomes empty:\n    - Autoplay suggested songs OR stop\n17. Repeat until user session ends",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
