      "text": "1. User searches car\n2. System shows available cars\n3. User selects car\n4. System locks car temporarily\n5. User enters details\n6. Payment initiated\n7. Booking confirmed\n8. User picks up car\n9. Trip starts\n10. Trip ends\n11. Invoice generated\n12. Payment/refund processed\n13. Car becomes available",
