      "updated": 1776052348073,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Rentalsystem will have multiple stores\nstores will have vehicles\nvehicle will be either available or not availabe\n\nUser will come to rentalsystem\nhe will search for Cars for a particular location\nSystem will check in stores at a location for avaialbe cars\nif cars are availble\nreturn to the user\n\nuser will select that car\npayment will be initiated\nbooking will be confirmed\n\nUser pick up the car\ntrip start\ntrip end\nSystem will calculate price and invoice will be generated\npayment happend\nVehicle is availabe again\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Rentalsystem will have multiple stores\nstores will have vehicles\nvehicle will be either available or not availabe\n\nUser will come to rentalsystem\nhe will search for Cars for a particular location\nSystem will check in stores at a location for avaialbe cars\nif cars are availble\nreturn to the user\n\nuser will select that car\npayment will be initiated\nbooking will be confirmed\n\nUser pick up the car\ntrip start\ntrip end\nSystem will calculate price and invoice will be generated\npayment happend\nVehicle is availabe again\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
